## Question Summary

Please provide a brief summary of your question or the clarification you need regarding a specific feature.

## Detailed Description

- **Feature Name/Description:**
  - Provide the name or a brief description of the feature in question.

- **Context/Background:**
  - Explain the context or background of your question. Why do you need clarification? Are there specific aspects of the feature that are confusing or unclear?

## Expected Outcome

- What do you hope to achieve or understand after receiving an answer to your question?

## Relevant Files/Links

- Include any relevant files, links, or screenshots that might help in understanding your question better.

## Additional Information

- Add any other information that might be helpful in answering your question.
